    "style": "Heading 2"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph",
    "index": 56,
    "text": "Figure 5: Confusion Matrix — Ensemble v3+v6 + TTA on unified val set (81.35%)",
    "style": "None"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph",
    "index": 59,
    "text": "Figure 6: Per-Class Emotion Accuracy — Ensemble v3+v6 + TTA (Overall: 81.35%)",
    "style": "None"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph",
    "index": 62,
    "text": "Note: Human accuracy on FER-2013 is approximately 65%. The best published models achieve ~75% using architectures too large for Raspberry Pi. Our model matches human-level performance with only 1.5M parameters.",
    "style": "None"
  },
  {
