    "style": "Heading 2"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph",
    "index": 116,
    "text": "Convert model to TFLite for faster Raspberry Pi inference.",
    "style": "List Paragraph"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph",
    "index": 117,
    "text": "Replace Haar Cascade with MediaPipe for more robust face detection.",
    "style": "List Paragraph"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph",
    "index": 118,
    "text": "Add LSTM temporal modeling for more stable emotion predictions.",
    "style": "List Paragraph"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph",
    "index": 119,
    "text": "✅ Multi-language TTS + STT support (Arabic + English) — COMPLETED.",
